  'UK Standard Visitor Visa for US Citizens: When You Need One & How to Apply (2026)',
  'Most Americans use the UK ETA for short visits — but some need a Standard Visitor Visa instead. Here''s when that applies, what documents you need, and how the application works in 2026.',
  'uk standard visitor visa us citizens',
  'Matthew Lin',
  8,
  '2026-03-04T00:00:00Z',
  'Most Americans use the UK ETA for short visits — but some need a Standard Visitor Visa instead. Here''s when that applies, what documents you need, and how the application works in 2026.',
  '[{"type":"paragraph","text":"The vast majority of Americans visiting the UK in 2026 will do so using the UK ETA — the £16 digital travel authorisation that covers short stays for tourism, business, family visits, and transit. But there''s a smaller group of US citizens for whom the ETA isn''t the right route, or isn''t an option at all."},{"type":"section","heading":"When Do US Citizens Need a Standard Visitor Visa?","items":[{"text":"Your ETA application was refused"},{"text":"You have a criminal conviction"},{"text":"You have a history of overstaying or immigration violations"},{"text":"You have been previously deported or banned from the UK"},{"text":"You want a long-term visitor visa (2-year, 5-year, or 10-year multi-entry)"},{"text":"Your circumstances are complex and you want human caseworker review"}]},{"type":"section","heading":"Document Checklist","items":[{"text":"Valid US passport — must cover your full stay"},{"text":"Completed online application form via the UKVI portal"},{"text":"Application fee: £115 (6 months), £400 (2 years), £771 (5 years), £963 (10 years)"},{"text":"Biometric enrollment at a UK Visa Application Centre in the US"},{"text":"Proof of financial means — recent bank statements"},{"text":"Proof of employment or income"},{"text":"Proof of accommodation — hotel bookings or host invitation letter"},{"text":"Return or onward travel ticket"},{"text":"Evidence of ties to the US — employment, property, family"}]},{"type":"section","heading":"Processing Times","items":[{"text":"Standard processing: approximately 3 weeks from biometric appointment"},{"text":"Priority processing (additional fee): approximately 5 business days"},{"text":"Super priority (same/next day): not available for US-based applicants"}]}]'::jsonb,
