  'Thinking of working in the UK as an American? Here''s every UK work visa route for US citizens in 2026 — Skilled Worker, Global Talent, Health & Care, Youth Mobility, and more — with salary thresholds, fees and processing times.',
  'uk work visa for americans',
  'Matthew Lin',
  10,
  '2026-03-04T00:00:00Z',
  'Thinking of working in the UK as an American? Here''s every UK work visa route for US citizens in 2026 — Skilled Worker, Global Talent, Health & Care, Youth Mobility, and more — with salary thresholds, fees and processing times.',
  '[{"type":"paragraph","text":"The United Kingdom remains one of the most attractive destinations in the world for American professionals — from finance in London to tech in Manchester, creative industries in Edinburgh, and healthcare across the country."},{"type":"paragraph","text":"The UK''s points-based immigration system, introduced in 2021, treats all non-UK nationals equally — including Americans. There''s no special relationship that gives US citizens a fast track to UK employment."},{"type":"section","heading":"Skilled Worker Visa — Key Requirements (2026)","items":[{"text":"Job offer from a UK employer holding a valid sponsorship licence","bold":["Job offer"]},{"text":"Minimum salary: £41,700 per year or the official going rate — whichever is higher","bold":["£41,700 per year"]},{"text":"Skill level: RQF Level 6 (roughly equivalent to a bachelor''s degree)"},{"text":"US citizens are automatically exempt from the English language requirement"},{"text":"Visa fee: £769 (up to 3 years) or £1,519 (more than 3 years)"},{"text":"Immigration Health Surcharge: £1,035 per year — paid upfront for full visa duration"},{"text":"Route to ILR after 5 years of continuous qualifying residence"}]},{"type":"section","heading":"Other Work Visa Routes","items":[{"text":"Health & Care Worker — lower fees (£304), IHS exempt; for qualified clinical professionals"},{"text":"Global Talent — no job offer needed; requires endorsement as leader in your field"},{"text":"Youth Mobility Scheme — ages 18-30, 2-year stay, any employer, no salary threshold"},{"text":"Innovator Founder — for entrepreneurs with endorsed innovative business plan"}]}]'::jsonb,
